ow can you initialize the following provider?


terraform {

required_providers {

aws = {

version = ">= 2.7.0"

source = "hashicorp/aws"

}

}

}

1 / 1 point

terraform aws init


terraform provider aws init


terraform init


terraform provider init

Correct
By using this command, we can initialize any provider.

